prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration of a funny and cute birthday card. In the center, cartoon versions of the couple from the reference photo are on a minimalist, idyllic beach. The scene is clean with simple elegant shapes and a soft pastel color palette.

Lao Lao (person on the left) is sitting on a beach towel, laughing joyfully with a classic boba milk tea in her hand. Jordan (person on the right) is standing behind her, playfully trying to build a sandcastle on top of her head using a small pail and shovel, with a mischievous, loving expression. The sandcastle is comically lopsided.

The background is a simple, cute beach with gentle, stylized waves and a clear sky. A few minimalist boba tapioca pearls are scattered in the sand like seashells.

Centered below the illustration, elegant, beautiful handwritten cursive script reads: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao"
